subject: Basketball (College)
NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
lead_paragraph: All four teams involved in Thursday’s day session in Lexington, Ky. — Butler, Bucknell, Marquette and Davidson — rose from relative obscurity to captivate the tournament in Marches past.
